                    <div class="modal-content">
                        <div class="modal-header">
                            <h4 class="modal-title" id="rulesModalLabel">Stockerdle rules</h4>
                            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="modal-body">
                            <div id="rules">
                                <h4 class="display-6">
                                    Rules
                                </h4>
                                <p class="h6">
                                    The goal of the game is to guess the mystery stock in 8 tries. Each guess must be a
                                    valid
                                    ticker symbol. Press enter to submit.
                                    <br>
                                    <br>
                                    After each guess, information will be give about the stock's market cap, price,
                                    stock
                                    exchange, and ticker symbol to help you narrow down your choices and get the mystery
                                    stock. You will have 8 tries to guess the stock. Good luck!
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <br>
                            <h4 class="display-6 mb-3">Examples</h4>
                            <div id="ticker">
                                <span class="bg-warning p-2">N</span>
                                <span class="bg-secondary p-2">F</span>
                                <span class="bg-secondary p-2">L</span>
                                <span class="bg-success p-2">X</span>
                                <p class=" mt-3">The N is in the ticker symbol, but not in the first spot, and the X is
                                    in
                                    the ticker symbol and in the last spot.</p>
                            </div>
                            <br>

                            <div id="exchange">
                                <span class="bg-success p-2">NASDAQ</span>
                                <p class=" mt-3">The green signifies that the stock exchange of the secret stock is
                                    NASDAQ.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <br>
                            <div id="cap">
                                <span class="bg-info p-2">$142.51 ↓</span>
                                <p class=" mt-3">The blue signifies that the secret stock's price is somehat close to
                                    $142.51, but not very close. The down arrow means that the price of the secret stock
                                    is
                                    less
                                    than $142.51. A gray would mean the guessed price is not close, yellow would mean it
                                    is
                                    close, and green means it is exceptionally close (so it is essentially correct).
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <br>

                            <div id="price">
                                <span class="bg-warning p-2">$94.1B ↑</span>
                                <p class="mt-3">The yellow signifies that the market cap of the secret stock is close to
                                    $94.1B, and the up arrow means that the secret stocks' market cap is greater than
                                    $94.1B
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <div id="tickerLength">
                                <span class="bg-secondary p-2">4 ↓</span>
                                <p class="mt-3">The gray signifies that the length of the ticker is not 4, and the arrow
                                    shows that it is less than 4.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

